sequenceDiagram
    participant Cliente
    participant API as Boundary HTTP
    participant Runtime as Logger Canônico
    participant Meta as Sidecar/Manifest
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant Admin as Provider Administrativo

    Cliente->>API: Request com ou sem X-Correlation-Id
    API->>API: Resolve correlation_id oficial
    API->>Runtime: Propaga correlation_id para logs
    Runtime->>Meta: Registra sidecar e manifest quando aplicavel
    API-->>Cliente: Response com X-Correlation-Id
    Cliente->>UI: Entrega correlation_id oficial
    UI->>API: Chamadas auxiliares com o mesmo id
    Admin->>Meta: Resolve familia de logs
    Admin->>Runtime: Le leitura via provider canônico
